				<td colspan="2"><span>Yeldema is light blue and has no ae and can be straight melee soloed if you have very good gear and buffs.  Harla dar is a nice one to solo, will need to bleed her manapool dry, then use cragwyrms to mellee her down and hope that she is not the summoning variety.  If you keep her mana at nothing (she regens mana very quickly) you will be able to keep her from gating.  It normally takes about 4-5 crag's to get the job done.  And even if harla does not summon, the crags do...so be careful.</span></td>
